})) 18. Kc1 {White wins a piece now due to the pin on the e7-knight. Black's counterplay is quickly extinguished. White wins a piece now due to the pin on the e7-knight. Black's counterplay is quickly extinguished. White wins a piece now due to the pin on the e7-knight. Black's counterplay is quickly extinguished. +⁠− White wins the piece and smoothly regroups to enjoy his extra piece.} O-O-O 19. Rxe7 Bxf3 20. gxf3 Qxf3 21. Qg3 $1 {The mate threat on c7 stops the counterplay. Black has no compensation for the piece. The mate threat on c7 stops the counterplay. Black has no compensation for the piece. The mate threat on c7 stops the counterplay. Black has no compensation for the piece.} Qc6 22. Kc2 Rd6 23. Rae1 Rhd8 24. R1e2 a5 25. Qe5 1-0


