{[%evp 11,138,-1,2,-1,9,1,1,-5,1,-3,0,-8,23,11,24,13,54,23,15,18,36,-27,16,-1,0,-1,8,0,26,-1,1,-1,0,-17,1,-1,1,-1,1,-16,-12,-21,-12,-23,-19,-27,-23,-31,-20,-25,-21,-40,-24,-43,-1,-36,-18,-55,-48,-62,-45,-54,-33,-55,-52,-65,-60,-57,-59,-57,-61,-62,-63,-160,-69,-78,-40,-108,-103,-88,-86,-157,-152,-181,-162,-317,-181,-320,-276,-304,-285,-317,-258,-376,-357,-366,-214,-366,-359,-386,-340,-381,-360,-376,-345,-388,-364,-1944,-1655,-2174,-1914,-1742,0,-1583,-2019,-1945,-1573,-29947,-29980,-29980,-29980,-29981,-29982,-29983,-29984,-29984,-29985,-29985,-29986] C65: Ruy Lopez: Berlin Defence (3...Nf6), unusual lines and 4 0-0 Bc5} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 {[%cal Bf1b5,Bb5a4,Ba4c2][%mdl 32]} Nf6 4. d3 Bc5 5. O-O Nd4 6. Nxd4 Bxd4 7. c3 Bb6 8. Ba4 {8.Na3 is a critical line. 8.Sa3 ist die kritische Fortsetzung.} c6 9. Bc2 $146 {The position is equal.} (9. Na3 d6 10. Bb3 (10. Bc2 Be6 11. Qe2 h6 12. Kh1 g5 13. Nc4 Bc7 14. Ne3 d5 15. Re1 Qe7 16. a4 O-O-O 17. Rb1 d4 18. Nf1 Bb6 19. Bd2 Bg4 20. f3 Be6 21. Ng3 Rhg8 22. b4 g4 23. a5 dxc3 24. Bxc3 Bd4 {Chapter Middlegames (3)-Game 3 Game 3 (48)}) 10... Be6 (10... a5 11. Nc4 Bc7 12. Bg5 h6 13. Bh4 g5 14. Bg3 h5 15. f3 Be6 16. Ne3 h4 17. Bf2 d5 18. Re1 Kf8 19. h3 Bb6 20. Qc2 Nh5 21. d4 exd4 22. cxd4 Nf4 23. Ng4 a4 24. Bxa4 dxe4 25. Rxe4 {10.a3 b6 11.ba5 h5_7469 (2760)-Deslandes,P (2811) Palma de Mallorca 2015 LEX-CD [FS1981/67] ½-½ (41)}) 11. Bxe6 fxe6 12. Nc4 O-O 13. Qb3 Re8 14. Bg5 Qc7 15. Kh1 Bc5 16. Qd1 d5 17. Nd2 Rf8 18. Qe2 a5 19. Bh4 Rae8 20. Rae1 Bd6 21. a4 Nd7 22. Nb3 b5 23. Ra1 Nb6 {13.c2 e5 14.e5 (2586)-R--- of B,F (2550) Budapest 2023 CHECK99 [John Watson] ½-½ (53)}) 9... d5 $146 ({Predecessor:} 9... O-O 10. Bg5 h6 11. Bh4 Re8 12. Nd2 d5 {Prevents Nd2-c4.} 13. h3 dxe4 14. dxe4 Bc7 15. a4 a5 {½-½ Nechaev,A (2303)-Chen,F (2302) RUS-ROW email 2018 [50]}) 10. exd5 Qxd5 11. Bb3 Qd6 {[%eval 23,20]} (11... Qd8 $142 {[%eval -8,21]}) 12. Na3 $11 {And now Na3-c4 would win.} Be6 13. Bg5 Bxb3 {[%eval 54,21]} (13... Nd7 $11 {[%eval 13,20] is superior.}) 14. axb3 {[%eval 23,23]} (14. Qxb3 $14 {[%eval 54,21]} O-O 15. Nc4) 14... O-O 15. Nc4 Qe6 16. Qe2 {[%eval -27,21]} (16. Re1 $14 {[%eval 36,21]}) 16... Rfe8 {[%eval 16,20]} (16... Nd5 {[%eval -27,21] is more appropriate.}) 17. Bxf6 Qxf6 18. Rfe1 {[%cal Od3d4]} Qd8 {Inhibits d3-d4.} 19. b4 (19. Nxe5 $2 f6 20. d4 fxe5 21. Qc4+ Kh8 22. Rxe5 Rxe5 23. dxe5 Qg5 $19) 19... f6 20. Qe4 Qd7 21. g3 Rad8 22. Rad1 g6 23. Nxb6 axb6 24. h4 Kg7 25. Qe3 b5 26. Qb6 (26. Kg2 {is interesting.} h5 27. Rd2 Re7 28. f3) 26... Re7 27. Qc5 Re6 28. Rd2 Rd6 29. Qb6 h5 30. Kg2 Qf7 31. Qe3 R8d7 32. f3 Qb3 {[%eval -1,21]} (32... Qe8 $15 {[%eval -43,24]}) 33. Qe2 {[%eval -36,23]} (33. Ree2 $11 {[%eval -1,21] was preferrable.}) 33... Qe6 34. Ra1 {[%eval -55,24]} (34. f4 $11 {[%eval -18,22]}) 34... Qg8 35. Qe3 Qd8 {[%cal Rd6d3]} 36. Rad1 $1 b6 {[%cal Bb7b6,Bb6c5,Bc5b4][%mdl 32]} 37. Kh2 Rd5 38. Kg2 c5 39. bxc5 bxc5 40. b3 b4 41. cxb4 cxb4 42. f4 {[%eval -160,20]} (42. Rc2 $15 {[%eval -63,25]}) 42... Re7 {[%eval -69,23]} (42... Qa8 $17 {[%eval -160,20]} 43. Qf3 exf4 44. gxf4 Qd8) 43. Re1 $15 Rdd7 {[%eval -40,23]} (43... Rd4 $17 {[%eval -78,22][%cal Oe5e4] White must now prevent ...e5-e4!} 44. Ree2 Rdd7) 44. Qf3 {[%eval -108,24] White is on the road to losing.} ({White should play} 44. Ree2 $1 $15 {[%eval -40,23]}) 44... exf4 $17 45. Rxe7+ Rxe7 46. gxf4 {[%eval -157,23][%mdl 4096] Endgame KQR-KQR} ({White should try} 46. Rf2 {[%eval -86,24]}) 46... Qd4 47. Re2 {[#]} Rd7 ({Stronger than} 47... Rxe2+ 48. Qxe2 Kf8 49. Qe4 Qb2+ 50. Kg3 $11) 48. f5 $2 {[%eval -317,25]} (48. Qg3 {[%eval -162,21]}) 48... Qxh4 $19 {Threatens to win with ...Qh4-g4+.} 49. fxg6 {[%eval -320,27]} (49. Re4 $142 {[%eval -181,22]} Qg5+ 50. Kh2) 49... Rd4 ({Worse is} 49... Kxg6 50. Qe4+ Qxe4+ 51. Rxe4 $17) 50. Re4 Rxe4 {Really sharp!} 51. dxe4 {KQ-KQ} Qg5+ ({Not} 51... Kxg6 52. Qf5+ Kh6 53. Kf3 $19) 52. Kh1 {[%eval -376,28]} (52. Kh3 $142 {[%eval -258,29]}) 52... Kxg6 {aiming for ...Qg5-h4+.} 53. Qd3 Qh4+ {[%eval -214,28]} (53... Qc1+ $142 {[%eval -366,29]} 54. Kg2 Qb2+ 55. Kg1 Qc3) 54. Kg2 $2 {[%eval -366,28]} (54. Kg1 {[%eval -214,28]}) 54... Qg4+ 55. Kh2 Qf4+ 56. Kh1 Qc1+ 57. Kg2 {[#]} Qb2+ 58. Kh1 Qc3 59. Qd5 {[%eval -1944,29]} (59. Qb1 {[%eval -364,23]}) 59... Qc1+ 60. Kh2 Qf4+ 61. Kh3 Qg4+ 62. Kh2 Qh4+ 63. Kg2 Qg5+ 64. Kh3 Qxd5 {Black mates.} 65. exd5 Kf5 66. Kh4 Ke5 67. Kxh5 Kxd5 68. Kg4 Kd4 69. Kf5 Kc3 {Weighted Error Value: White=0.39/Black=0.12 (very precise)} 0-1


