d7 Kd6 47. Be8 h4 48. Kd4 Kc7 49. Bg6 e3 50. fxe3 fxe3 51. Kxe3 Kb6 52. Bd3 Bg2 53. Kf4 h3 54. Kg3 Ka7 55. Bf5 Kxa6 56. Bxh3 Bc6 {with a drawish endgame with a drawish endgame}) 46... f3 47. Kd2 (47. Be8 e3 48. fxe3 f2 49. Bb5 Ke4 50. Kd2 Kf3 $11) 47... Kf4 48. Bd7 (48. Ke1 e3) 48... e3+ 49. Ke1 (49. fxe3+ Kg3) 49... Be4 50. Bc8 Bd3 51. Bb7 exf2+ 52. Kxf2 Bxa6 $11) 43. Rxc5 Kxc5 44. Ke3 $18 {White has stopped ...f5-f4 and wins. White has stopped ...f5-f4 and wins.} Bc6 45. Bh5 Kd5 (45... Kb6 46. Bg6 Bd7 47. Kd4 $18) 46. a7 Ke5 (46... Kc5 47. Bg6) 47. f4+ {Arsovic,Goran: '!'} (47. f4+ gxf4+ 48. gxf4+ Kf6 (48... Kd5 49. Be8 Ba8 50. Bd7) 49. Be8 Ba8 50. Bd7 Kg6 51. Kd4 Kf6 52. Kc5 {[%cal Rd7c6]} e3 53. Bb5 $18) 1-0


