al knight offers him chances for freeing his position with a central break. <xml:en>An interesting structure. If White manages to block the e- and c-pawns properly (and as his greatest dream, to exchange the dark-squared bishops) then he will get a clear advantage. But Black's strong central knight offers him chances for freeing his position with a central break.</:en/xml>'' An interesting structure. If White manages to block the e- and c-pawns properly (and as his greatest dream, to exchange the dark-squared bishops) then he will get a clear advantage. But Black's strong central knight offers him chances for freeing his position with a central break. David Cummings: 'Marin,Mihail: 'An interesting structure. If White manages to block the e- and c-pawns properly (and as his greatest dream, to exchange the dark-squared bishops) then he will get a clear advantage. But Black's strong central knight offers him chances for freeing his position with a central break.''} 12. Na4 {David Cummings: '<xml:en>The knight is heading for c5, preventing ...<sym>Q</sym>b6 at the same time.</:en/xml> Marin,Mihail: 'The knight is heading for c5, preventing ...b6 at the same time. <xml:en>The knight is heading for c5, preventing ...<sym>Q</sym>b6 at the same time.</:en/xml>'' The knight is heading for c5, preventing ...b6 at the same time. David Cummings: 'Marin,Mihail: 'The knight is heading for c5, preventing ...b6 at the same time.''} (12. Ne4 Qb6 {David Cummings: '<xml:en>allows Black to activate his play:</:en/xml> Marin,Mihail: 'allows Black to activate his play: <xml:en>allows Black to activate his play:</:en/xml>'' allows Black to activate his play: David Cummings: 'Marin,Mihail: 'allows Black to activate his play:''} 13. Rd1 Ba6 14. Ne5 Rad8 15. Be3 Nxe3 {David Cummings: '<xml:en>The start of premature counterplay.</:en/xml> Marin,Mihail: 'The start of premature counterplay. <xml:en>The start of premature counterplay.</:en/xml>'' The start of premature counterpl