 it. Should Black play 39...Rxg2, or does the solution lie elsewhere? --- ANSWER:'} Nd6 $1 {ChessBase: 'Cyrus Lakdawala: '!!' Cyrus Lakdawala: 'We witness a unique alignment of geometric stars. How inadequate our own chess feels when measured against a player of monumental natural talent. It isn't as if Carlsen has large reserves of capital to invest, but here he offers a knight, which can't be touched. '' ChessBase: 'Cyrus Lakdawala: '!!' '!!' Cyrus Lakdawala: 'We witness a unique alignment of geometric stars. How inadequate our own chess feels when measured against a player of monumental natural talent. It isn't as if Carlsen has large reserves of capital to invest, but here he offers a knight, which can't be touched. ''} ({Carlsen avoids Wei's insidious trap} 39... Rxg2 $2 40. Nc6 $1 c2 $4 (40... Ng7 $1 {is forced}) 41. Ra7+ Kc8 42. Kb6 $1 c1=Q {(this extra queen isn't of much help for Black)} 43. Rc7# {.}) (39... Rd2 $2 {Kapnisis,Spyridon} 40. Nc6 Kc8 41. Ra7 $1 Ng7 42. Re7 $1 Ne6+ 43. Kc4 Nd8 44. Na7+ Kb8 45. Kxc3 $11) 40. Nc6 {ChessBase: 'Cyrus Lakdawala: '!' Cyrus Lakdawala: 'When heavily stressed, our mind can either suffer panic/depression, or turn courageous/inventive, as we see here. On the one hand we are paralyzed, and on the other, we experience a kind of hyperconscious state, where we turn our resistance into a genetically enhanced super-soldier.'' ChessBase: 'Cyrus Lakdawala: '!' '!' Cyrus Lakdawala: 'When heavily stressed, our mind can either suffer panic/depression, or turn courageous/inventive, as we see here. On the one hand we are paralyzed, and on the other, we experience a kind of hyperconscious state, where we turn our resistance into a genetically enhanced super-soldier.'' ChessBase: 'White is still in the game. He threatens to win a piece with Ra7+.' ChessBase: 'White is still in the game. He threatens to win a piece with Ra7+.'} ({ChessBase: 'Cyrus Lakdawala: 'In inferior positions it's crucial to remain alert yet calm, in a state of prepa