00:00] [#]} Rac8 $36 {[%emt 0:00:14] ...d3 is the strong threat. [#] Black is more active. White must now prevent ... a7-a6.} 31. Be5 $1 {[%emt 0:01:27] [#]} d3 $1 {[%emt 0:00:23] Strongly threatening ...a6. Threatens to win with ... a7-a6.} (31... a6 32. Nxd4 Bxd4 (32... Bxd6 {[%eval -1,22] 32...Bc5xd4 -0.57} 33. Bf6 $11) 33. Bxd4 $11) (31... Kf7 $5 {simplifies} 32. Nxd4 Bxd6 33. Nf3 Kg6) 32. Bf6 {[%eval -154,27] [%emt 0:05:00] Wards off a6} (32. Rd1 $1 $15 {[%eval -39,24]}) 32... Rd7 $17 {[%emt 0:00:09]} 33. Bxg5 {[%emt 0:00:28]} a6 {[%emt 0:14:01]} ({And not} 33... Bxd6 34. Nxd6 Rxd6 35. Rd1 $17) 34. Nc3 {[%emt 0:00:12]} Bxd6 {[%eval -113,25] [%emt 0:00:19]} ({Black should play} 34... Rxd6 {[%eval -150,24] ... d2 would now be deadly. Strongly threatening ...d3-d2.} 35. Ne4 Re6 36. Nxc5 Rxc5) 35. Ne4 {[%emt 0:02:03] And now Nf6+ would win. Nf6+ is the strong threat.} Be7 {[%emt 0:01:13] aiming for ...Bxg5. Hoping for ...Bxg5. &Nero is more active.} 36. Rd1 $2 {[%eval -605,23] [%emt 0:01:37]} (36. Be3 $17 {[%eval -120,23]}) 36... Bxg5 $19 {[%emt 0:00:00] Remove Defender, Deflection. Black is clearly winning. [#] Deflection. Black is clearly winning. Black is clearly winning.} 37. Nxg5 {[%emt 0:00:02]} d2 {[%emt 0:00:00] (  ...Rc1)} 38. Kf1 {[%emt 0:00:33]} Re7 {[%emt 0:00:00] Weighted Error Value: White=0.44/Black=0.03 (flawless) Weighted Error Value: White=0.39/Black=0.09 (flawless) . Loses game:  White=1  ---  Mistake:   White=4  Black=2  Inaccurate:   White=1  Black=1  OK:   White=12  Black=15  Best:   White=2   Black=2. Weighted Error Value: White=0.45/Black=0.04 (flawless)} 0-1


