1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 a6 6. Be3 e6 7. f3 b5 8. Qd2 Nbd7 9. g4 b4 10. Nce2 h6 11. O-O-O Qc7 12. h4 d5 13. exd5 Nxd5 14. Nf4 Nxe3 15. Qxe3 Qe5 16. Qd2 Bc5 {Diagramm [#] Black has misplayed a sharp line of the English Attack and is now quickly punished for it:} 17. Nf5 $1 {Starting the action.} O-O (17... exf5 18. Re1 {simply loses the Q.}) 18. Re1 Qb8 19. Nxg7 $1 {The energetic follow-up.} b3 (19... Kxg7 20. Nh5+ Kh7 21. Bd3+ f5 22. Rxe6 {and White's attack wins easily.}) 20. axb3 Qb4 21. c3 Qxb3 22. Ngh5 (22. Ngxe6 $5 fxe6 23. Nxe6 {also looks good.}) 22... Rb8 23. Nd3 Ba3 24. Rh2 Bb7 (24... Qa2 {was the final defensive try.}) 25. Kb1 Bxf3 26. Qxh6 Qxc3 27. Re5 1-0


