1. d4 d5 2. Nf3 e6 3. c4 c5 4. cxd5 exd5 5. g3 Nf6 6. Bg2 Be7 7. O-O O-O 8. dxc5 Bxc5 9. Qc2 Ne4 10. Nc3 Nxc3 11. bxc3 h6 12. Rd1 Qb6 13. Rb1 Qa5 14. Nd2 Qc7 15. Nb3 Bb4 16. Bb2 Nd7 17. Rxd5 Nb6 18. Rd4 Be7 19. c4 Bf6 {Diagram #} 20. c5 $1 {With this positional exchange sacrifice White keeps a strong initiative.} Bxd4 ({In case of} 20... Nd7 {White can simply retreat with} 21. Rdd1 {and c4 is no longer hanging.}) 21. Nxd4 Nd7 22. c6 $1 bxc6 (22... Nb6 {is met by} 23. Nb5 $1 Qb8 (23... Qe7 24. Ba3) (23... Qd8 24. cxb7) 24. c7 {trapping the Q.}) 23. Nxc6 Kh8 24. Qd2 {Threatening 25.Qxh6.} Kh7 25. Ba3 Ba6 (25... Re8 26. Bd6) 26. Bd6 Qc8 27. Bxf8 (27. Bxf8 {and Black resigned as both} Nxf8 ({and} 27... Qxf8 28. Qxd7) 28. Ne7 {lose more material.}) 1-0


