{Vidit,S: 'China had been our main competitor in the Asian championship and needless to say this was a very crucial match for the final standings.''China had been our main competitor in the Asian championship and needless to say this was a very crucial match for the final standings. Vidit,Santosh Gujrathi: 'Vidit,S/Quintiliano,R: 'China had been our main competitor in the Asian championship and needless to say this was a very crucial match for the final standings.' Vidit,S: 'China had been our main competitor in the Asian championship and needless to say this was a very crucial match for the final standings.''' China had been our main competitor in the Asian championship and needless to say this was a very crucial match for the final standings.  Vidit,S: 'Vidit,Santosh Gujrathi: 'China had been our main competitor in the Asian championship and needless to say this was a very crucial match for the final standings. ''} 1. e4 {Vidit,S Vidit,S Vidit,S Vidit,S/Quintiliano,R Vidit,S Vidit,S: 'Vidit,Santosh Gujrathi Vidit,Santosh Gujrathi: 'Vidit,S Vidit,S Vidit,S/Quintiliano,R Vidit,S/Quintiliano,R Vidit,S'' Vidit,S: 'Vidit,Santosh Gujrathi Vidit,Santosh Gujrathi Vidit,Santosh Gujrathi: 'Vidit,S Vidit,S Vidit,S/Quintiliano,R Vidit,S/Quintiliano,R Vidit,S''} e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Bc5 4. d3 Nf6 5. c3 O-O 6. O-O d5 {Vidit,S/Quintiliano,R: '!?' Vidit,S: 'The most direct and concrete attempt to equalise against the Italian. The resulting position leads to the e5-point becoming the main battlefield. Most of the following moves from both sides either directly or indirectly influence control of the e5-point.''The most direct and concrete attempt to equalise against the Italian. The resulting position leads to the e5-point becoming the main battlefield. Most of the following moves from both sides either directly or indirectly influence control of the e5-point. Vidit,Santosh Gujrathi: 'Vidit,S/Quintiliano,R: '!?' '!?' Vidit,S/Quintiliano,R: 'The most direct and concrete attempt to equalise against the Italian. The resulting position leads to the e5-point becoming the main battlefield. Most of the following moves from both sides either directly or indirectly influence control of the e5-point.' Vidit,S: 'The most direct and concrete attempt to equalise against the Italian. The resulting position leads to the e5-point becoming the main battlefield. Most of the following moves from both sides either directly or indirectly influence control of the e5-point.''' The most direct and concrete attempt to equalise against the Italian. The resulting position leads to the e5-point becoming the main battlefield. Most of the following moves from both sides either directly or indirectly influence control of the e5-point.  Vidit,S: 'Vidit,Santosh Gujrathi: 'The most direct and concrete attempt to equalise against the Italian. The resulting position leads to the e5-point becoming the main battlefield. Most of the following moves from both sides either directly or indirectly influence control of the e5-point. ''} 7. exd5 Nxd5 {Vidit,S: 'White already has a choice to make here. He has a wide variety of options at his disposal, leading to various kinds of strategically complex, yet balanced positions.''White already has a choice to make here. He has a wide variety of options at his disposal, leading to various kinds of strategically complex, yet balanced positions. Vidit,Santosh Gujrathi: 'Vidit,S/Quintiliano,R: 'White already has a choice to make here. He has a wide variety of options at his disposal, leading to various kinds of strategically complex, yet balanced positions.' Vidit,S: 'White already has a choice to make here. He has a wide variety of options at his disposal, leading to various kinds of strategically complex, yet balanced positions.''' White already has a choice to make here. He has a wide variety of options at his disposal, leading to various kinds of strategically complex, yet balanced positions.  Vidit,S: 'Vidit,Santosh Gujrathi: 'White already